# Globally Distributed, Ultra-Scalable Voice & Video Calling Platform

## WebRTC + coturn Architecture Specification for 100M+ Users

> **Target Scale**: 100M+ registered users В· 10M+ concurrent WebSocket connections В· 3M+ concurrent active calls
> **SLA**: 99.995% availability В· <120ms average global call setup latency
> **Stack**: Node.js В· TypeScript В· Fastify В· Socket.io В· Redis Cluster В· PostgreSQL В· Kafka В· coturn В· Kubernetes
> **Regions**: US-EAST (Ashburn) В· EU-WEST (Frankfurt) В· AP-SOUTH (Mumbai) В· AP-EAST (Tokyo)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This document is the **definitive backend distributed systems specification**. No frontend UI/UX is included. Every decision is production-grade with explicit scalability reasoning and trade-off analysis.

