## 5. Layer 4 вҖ” Media Layer (WebRTC)

### 5.1 P2P Media Architecture

```
User A в—„в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ DTLS-SRTP (P2P direct or via TURN relay) в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв–ә User B
   в”Ӯ                                                                        в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  ICE candidate gathering                              ICE gathering    в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ                          в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ   в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ host candidates  в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ host candidates   в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ srflx (STUN)     в”Ӯ  в—„в”Җв”Җ trickled via в”Җв”Җв–ә   в”Ӯ srflx (STUN)      в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ relay (TURN)     в”Ӯ      signaling layer     в”Ӯ relay (TURN)      в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ                          в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ   в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ                                                                        в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  ICE connectivity checks:                                              в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  1. host вҶ” host        (LAN вҖ” fastest, ~1ms)                          в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  2. srflx вҶ” srflx      (STUN вҖ” P2P through NAT, ~20ms)               в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  3. srflx вҶ” host       (asymmetric NAT, ~25ms)                        в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  4. relay вҶ” relay      (TURN fallback вҖ” last resort, ~80ms)           в”Ӯ
```

### 5.2 ICE Strategy: STUN-First

**Policy**: `iceTransportPolicy: 'all'` with UDP candidates prioritized.

| ICE Path | Bandwidth Cost | % of Calls | Latency |
|----------|---------------|------------|---------|
| P2P direct (host/srflx) | $0 | ~50% | <20ms |
| P2P through NAT (STUN) | $0 | ~30% | 20-50ms |
| TURN relay (UDP) | $0.02/GB | ~15% | 50-100ms |
| TURN relay (TCP/TLS) | $0.02/GB | ~5% | 80-150ms |

### 5.3 Codec Negotiation Strategy

**Audio (all calls):**

| Codec | Bitrate | Use Case | Priority |
|-------|---------|----------|----------|
| Opus | 6-128 kbps | Primary codec вҖ” adaptive, low-latency | 1 (highest) |
| Opus CBR 32kbps | 32 kbps | Low-bandwidth mode | Auto-selected |
| Opus CBR 16kbps | 16 kbps | Ultra-low bandwidth fallback | Auto-selected |

**Video (video calls only):**

| Codec | Bitrate Range | Use Case | Priority |
|-------|-------------|----------|----------|
| VP9 | 150kbps - 2.5Mbps | Primary вҖ” better compression | 1 |
| H.264 | 200kbps - 3Mbps | Fallback вҖ” hardware accel | 2 |
| VP8 | 200kbps - 2Mbps | Legacy fallback | 3 |
| AV1 | 100kbps - 2Mbps | Future вҖ” best compression | 4 (when available) |

### 5.4 SRTP Encryption

| Layer | Protocol | Key Exchange |
|-------|----------|-------------|
| Signaling transport | TLS 1.3 (WSS) | ECDHE |
| DTLS handshake | DTLS 1.2+ | ECDHE |
| Media encryption | SRTP (AES-128-CM) | Derived from DTLS |
| TURN relay | DTLS over TURN | Same as P2P вҖ” TURN cannot decrypt |

