### 12.2 Conflict Resolution

- If both users request upgrade simultaneously: first-writer-wins via Redis CAS.
- If upgrade fails within 15s: revert to `AUDIO_ONLY_CONNECTED`, no call disruption.
- During upgrade, audio stream continues uninterrupted on existing ICE connection.

