## 20. Bandwidth Cost Optimization

| Strategy | Savings | Implementation |
|----------|---------|----------------|
| UDP-first ICE | 40% TURN cost | Client `iceTransportPolicy: 'all'`, UDP prioritized |
| Adaptive bitrate (TWCC/REMB) | 30% bandwidth | Sender-side bandwidth estimation |
| TURN allocation pooling | 15% cost | Reuse across ICE restarts |
| Regional TURN selection | 25% egress | Route to same-region relay |
| Audio-only fallback | 80% bandwidth | Auto-switch when <200kbps |
| Codec optimization | 20% bandwidth | Prefer VP9/AV1 + Opus |
| Short-call optimization | 10% cost | Skip TURN for <5s calls |

